Thank-You Note for Research

All research topics are only possible owing to previous wonderful educational training and amazingly talented collaborators.

I am looking forward to new opportunities of funding, collaborations, and random inspiring chats.

  • 01st Jan 2025: I firmly believe that embodied intelligence can only thrive when we reframe our design philosophystarting with sensing and perception before actuation. Natural species exist to perceive the vibrance of the world, not merely to work until death. We once took pride in changing the world, but in truth, we seldom did. The world remains the sameit is our perception that evolves.

  • 19th May 2024: I couldn't agree more with one of the perspectives shared in ICRA2024 Robotics Debates that the digital world is shading out while the analog world is returning.
